libgtk2-unique-perl (0.06-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix: Segfault on starting second instance (Closes: RT-120115)
  * Fix: Compilation warnings/stack smash from incompatible pointer type
  * d/control: Bump debhelper compatibility level to 12
  * d/control: Add Vcs-Browser/Vcs-Git links to official GNOME GitLab instance
  * d/control: Add autopkgtest-pkg-perl test suite
  * d/rules: Added future=+lfs hardening=+all reproducible=+fixfilepath flags
  * d/watch: Update to version 4 and adjust regex for new GitLab repository
  * Change Maintainer to Ásbrú Project Team and Uploader to Peter J. Mello
  * Insert proper Build-Depends package versions
  * Declare compliance with Debian Policy 4.3.0
  * Add lintian override for debian-watch-does-not-check-gpg-signature
  * Add local options directive to clean source tree patches after build
  * Add upstream metadata file for UMEGAYA inclusion

 -- Peter J. Mello <admin@petermello.net>  Fri, 07 Jun 2019 18:52:39 -0700

